[package]
name = "openasio"
version = "1.0.0"
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Safe host-side wrapper for OpenASIO drivers"

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"
anyhow = "1.0"

[dependencies.openasio-sys]
path = "../openasio-sys"

[package]
name = "openasio-sys"
version = "1.0.0"
edition = "2021"
links = "openasio"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Raw FFI for the OpenASIO ABI"

[build-dependencies]
cc = "1.1"

[dependencies]
libloading = "0.8"
